title: House of the Dragon S1E9 Synopsis
description:
Make your friends green with envy over your knowledge of the Green Council.

When published, this is audio-only, but within 48 hours it becomes playable as a video on Spotify (and YouTube).

All season long, tune in Mondays at 6 pm eastern for Review episodes   with Sean and Saturdays at 3 pm eastern for Preview (spoiler-filled)   episodes with special guests.
